Leia Organa is incarcerated onboard the Death Star. When she fails to yield the location of the Rebel Alliance's hidden base, her home planet, Alderaan, is ordered destroyed by Grand Moff Wilhuff Tarkin. Bail Organa is killed in the planet's destruction.
